## Tools

- **anki-ai**: headless Anki CLI at `~/.local/bin/anki-ai`.
  Auth: `~/.config/anki-ai/auth.json` (pre-configured). Collection: `~/.local/share/Anki2/`.
  Use the `anki-cards` skill for full procedure.

- **Obsidian vault**: `{{ obsidian_vault }}`
  Use the `obsidian-note` skill for full procedure.
  Vault contains `AGENTS.md` with conventions.
